trans-unit.source: Indicates the first week of the year to use when calling date-related functions.
trans-unit.target: Angir den første uken i året som skal brukes når du kaller dato-relaterte funksjoner.

trans-unit.source: When you call date-related functions, you can use the following enumeration members in your code in place of the actual values.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller dato-relaterte funksjoner, kan du bruke følgende opplisting medlemmer i koden i stedet for de faktiske verdiene.

trans-unit.source: Some date-related functions take a `DayOfWeek` argument, a `WeekOfYear` argument, or both.
trans-unit.target: Noen funksjoner for dato-relaterte tar en `DayOfWeek` argumentet, et `WeekOfYear` argumentet eller begge deler.

trans-unit.source: The `FirstWeekOfYear` enumeration specifies the valid values for the `WeekOfYear` arguments, as well as the possible return values from the functions.
trans-unit.target: Den `FirstWeekOfYear` opplisting angir gyldige verdier for den `WeekOfYear` argumenter, i tillegg til mulige returverdier fra funksjonene.

trans-unit.source: The `WeekOfYear` argument takes the `FirstWeekOfYear` enumeration members.
trans-unit.target: Den `WeekOfYear` argumentet tar det `FirstWeekOfYear` opplisting medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: The first week that has at least four days in the new year.
trans-unit.target: Den første uken som har minst fire dager i det nye året.

trans-unit.source: This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFourDays" name="vbFirstFourDays" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Dette medlemmet tilsvarer Visual Basic konstanten <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFourDays" name="vbFirstFourDays" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The first full week of the year.
This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFullWeek" name="vbFirstFullWeek" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Dette medlemmet tilsvarer Visual Basic konstanten <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFullWeek" name="vbFirstFullWeek" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The week in which January 1 occurs (default).
This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstJan1" name="vbFirstJan1" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Dette medlemmet tilsvarer Visual Basic konstanten <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstJan1" name="vbFirstJan1" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The weekspecified in your system settings as the first week of the year.
trans-unit.target: Weekspecified i systeminnstillingene som den første uken i året.

trans-unit.source: This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbUseSystem" name="vbUseSystem" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Dette medlemmet tilsvarer Visual Basic konstanten <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbUseSystem" name="vbUseSystem" href=""> </xref>.
